OL,3,CAmbulance critical incident stood down
OL,4,Cbut 'significant' pressure remains
OL,6,FThe Welsh Ambulance Service has stood
OL,7,Fdown the critical incident it declared
OL,8,Fon Monday evening but says
OL,9,F'significant' pressure remains.
OL,11,FIt comes after people were urged by
OL,12,Fhealth bosses to avoid setting off
OL,13,Ffireworks and to drink responsibly on
OL,14,FNew Year's Eve in order to reduce
OL,15,Fpressure on the NHS.
OL,17,FBosses apologised to patients who have
OL,18,Fwaited "far too long" for an ambulance
OL,19,Fover the last 48 hours during one of
OL,20,Fthe busiest times of year for
OL,21,Femergency workers.
