OL,3,CAmbulance critical incident stood down
OL,4,Cbut 'significant' pressure remains
OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservatives said the
OL,7,Fcritical incident "highlights Labour's
OL,8,Fdisastrous record and mismanagement of
OL,9,Fthe NHS here in Wales."
OL,11,FThe service said it declared a
OL,12,Fcritical incident on Monday (30
OL,13,FDecember 2024) night as a result of
OL,14,F"extreme pressure" on the 999 system
OL,15,Fand extensive hospital handover
OL,16,Fdelays, exacerbated by a rising number
OL,17,Fof viruses such as flu, norovirus and
OL,18,FCovid-19.
