OL,3,CAmbulance critical incident stood down
OL,4,Cbut 'significant' pressure remains
OL,6,FCritical incident declarations are
OL,7,Frare, with the last one coming in
OL,8,FDecember 2020 when high demand,
OL,9,Fparticularly in south east Wales
OL,10,Fprompted concern from bosses.
OL,12,FOn New Year's day morning this year,
OL,13,Fthe critical incident was stood down
OL,14,Fafter the ambulance service said it
OL,15,Fhad taken a number of additional
OL,16,Fmeasures to mitigate pressures using
OL,17,F'well rehearsed plans".
