OL,6,FWelsh Conservative Shadow Cabinet
OL,7,FSecretary for Health and Social Care,
OL,8,FJames Evans MS, said: "The recent
OL,9,Fdeclaration of a critical incident by
OL,10,Fthe Welsh Ambulance Service highlights
OL,11,FLabour's disastrous record and
OL,12,Fmismanagement of the NHS here in Wales.
OL,14,F"This is not just a winter crisis`it's
OL,15,Fa glaring symptom of long-term
OL,16,Ffailures under Labour in Wales.
OL,17,FPatients waiting in distress and
OL,18,Foverstretched frontline workers
OL,19,Fdeserve far better.
