OL,6,F"Under Labour, Wales is broken. It's
OL,7,Ftime for real leadership and concrete
OL,8,Faction to fix these systemic issues
OL,9,Fonce and for all."
OL,11,FOn Tuesday, a Welsh Government
OL,12,Fspokesperson said that urgent and
OL,13,Femergency care services "continue to
OL,14,Fsee high levels of demand this winter.
OL,16,F"Increase in flu cases has further
OL,17,Fadded pressure during the Christmas
OL,18,Fperiod and resulted in action being
OL,19,Ftaken by health boards including
OL,20,Fprevention and control measures.
