OL,6,F"We are continuing to drive our 50-day
OL,7,Fchallenge to integrate health and
OL,8,Fsocial care services and help improve
OL,9,Fpatient flow through hospitals and
OL,10,Ftackle ambulance handover delays.
OL,12,F"We have invested more than #180m in
OL,13,Fadditional funds this year to help
OL,14,Fsafely manage more people in the
OL,15,Fcommunity, avoid ambulance transport
OL,16,Fand admission to hospital focusing on
OL,17,Fthe right care, in the right place,
OL,18,Ffirst time."
