OL,6,FThe Welsh Ambulance Service appealed
OL,7,Fto people who are experiencing flu-
OL,8,Flike symptoms to stay at home in order
OL,9,Fto limit the spread, as well as
OL,10,Fwashing hands regularly and keeping
OL,11,Fyour distance from vulnerable people.
OL,13,F"For anyone under the weather after
OL,14,FNew Year's Eve celebrations, consider
OL,15,Fwhat you can do at home to self-care,
OL,16,Fincluding for common ailments like
OL,17,Fcoughs, sore throats and diarrhoea.
